name: Serious Fox #3 - Fox with Hat
description:
Introducing 'Serious Fox #3', the first fox with a hat in the collection!

It consists of an image based on a fox in the 'Pixel Art' art style.

With the purchase of this NFT, you will be given the image in PNG with dimensions of 8000x8000 (8K).

I look forward to your purchase, Chrone.
